{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_03_03",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雑誌のグラビア撮影と取材当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、大人の恋愛って言っても\n人それぞれですよね",
      "startTime": 6.2999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.5666670959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは大人だから～とか考えずに、好きだなって\n思ったら、自分の気持ちに素直に行動しますね",
      "startTime": 12.266667064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.7333335083
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.7333334764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛観ですか？　そうですね……\nいい人がいれば、自分に嘘はつきたくないです",
      "startTime": 21.7333334764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "でも今は、恋愛していなくてもファンのみなさんに\n囲まれて、アイドルでいられることが幸せですし",
      "startTime": 29.4535529856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.7666668416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（さすがに本番になると）\n（読者層にあわせてしっかり語るんだな）",
      "startTime": 35.8666668098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.3333335083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "――読者からの質問ですか？\nんー……好きな人の前で素が見せられない",
      "startTime": 42.3000001431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.0666676045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "別に無理に見せる必要はないと思いますよ",
      "startTime": 48.0666676045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.2666698933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "素のままでいて、それでもずーっと愛される人なんて\n滅多にいないんじゃないかな？",
      "startTime": 56.5333365281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人には可愛く思われたい！　って\n自分を取り繕っちゃう気持ち、kanaも分かります～",
      "startTime": 61.9666698615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.3000032266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな相談者さんのこと\nkanaは可愛いな～って思いますけどね",
      "startTime": 68.4000031948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.1000032266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "きっと相手もそう思ってるから\n悩む必要はないんじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 74.4000031948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、素ってさ、隠しているつもりでも心を許した\n人には、勝手に見せてしまっているものだと思いますし",
      "startTime": 83.0000031948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.4000032266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかしてこれは、kanaさんの）\n（本音なのかな……？　お、そろそろ休憩か――）",
      "startTime": 89.9666698615,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5933.331330600012,
          "startTime": 95.9000011921
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.6666699092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、さっきのインタビュー良かったです！\nスタッフの方もいい記事になるとおっしゃってました",
      "startTime": 100.4666678269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.4999991576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あったりまえでしょ～！\n新規ファン獲得に向けて練りに練ってきた回答だし",
      "startTime": 105.5666678269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.9999991576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "kanaはプロなんだからファンの期待も\n周りの期待も超えるの",
      "startTime": 113.2000011603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "そのためには\nマネージャーの期待も超えていかないとね",
      "startTime": 116.9000011603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.9333324909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……そこで一つ聞きたいのですが……",
      "startTime": 119.9333324909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.4333324909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "何？　言ってみ\n今のkanaは機嫌がいいから答えてあげる",
      "startTime": 126.6666678269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのインタビューって\nまさか実体験に基づいてたりしませんよね……？",
      "startTime": 131.9235285133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　な、何言ってんの！　同年代の支持を\n得るために作ってきたって言ったっしょ！！",
      "startTime": 141.9333405971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それならいいんです\nでも、あまりにも具体的だったので",
      "startTime": 146.8914922661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "おい、kanaのことナメてんの？\nあれくらいいつもやってるから",
      "startTime": 153.1000133673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "それともいつものkanaのインタビューが\n悪いって言いたい？",
      "startTime": 158.6000184535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……先日恋愛解禁だ～と言っていたので\n恋人が出来たとか勘ぐってしまって……",
      "startTime": 165.9333578903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？　ほんっとうにポンコツマネージャーは\nkanaのことなんも分かってないよね～",
      "startTime": 173.9666749476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "別に分かってもらわなくてもいいけどさ\nあんなの冗談に決まってんじゃん",
      "startTime": 180.8354980273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "今、アイドルとしても、スリクスとしても\nkanaはそんなことしてる場合じゃないし",
      "startTime": 188.0999960738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "ポンコツマネージャーでも分かるでしょ？\n安心しなって。しばらくは恋愛する気なんてないから",
      "startTime": 194.266676982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan023.m4a",
      "text": "再びBIG4に返り咲くまでは、ね\nてか、こんな暑苦しいこと言わせんな",
      "startTime": 204.1666830855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……さすがですよ\nとはいえ、将来素敵な恋愛が出来るといいですね",
      "startTime": 211.6869413068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan024.m4a",
      "text": "なっ、何言ってんの！\nあんた今のkanaの話聞いてた！？",
      "startTime": 218.1666881718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan025.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーがアイドルに恋愛をそそのかすなって",
